1
00:00:09,292 --> 00:00:10,585
This is a big job.
这是个大工程.

2
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:14,078
But we can do it.
但是我们能做好.

3
00:00:15,559 --> 00:00:18,289
Klara Kovak, here we come.
Klara Kovak,我们来了.

4
00:00:48,587 --> 00:00:51,046
Nancy, Yvonne. Do come in. 
Nancy,Yvonne.请进.

5
00:00:53,754 --> 00:00:56,147
It's nice, but it's not quite right.
这房子装修得挺好,但是感觉不对.

6
00:00:56,473 --> 00:00:58,369
We've had several decorators come in,
我们请了几位装潢师,

7
00:00:58,530 --> 00:01:01,406
but so far, it's been a disappointment.
但到目前为止, 结果还是令人失望.

8
00:01:03,828 --> 00:01:04,835
Notice the colors. 
注意下颜色.

9
00:01:05,817 --> 00:01:07,180
They simply won't do.
根本不行.

10
00:01:07,417 --> 00:01:09,768
I can't bear to look at them...
我简直无法忍受去看他们...

11
00:01:20,700 --> 00:01:23,999
Antonio and I hired a firm to fix the walls.
Antonio和我雇了个公司来修理墙壁.

12
00:01:24,150 --> 00:01:27,068
Well, we came home to find the kitchen completely ruined.
Well,我们回家后发现厨房彻底给毁了.

13
00:01:27,738 --> 00:01:30,124
Do you know what they said to me?
你知道他们对我说什么吗?

14
00:01:32,575 --> 00:01:33,192
From then on, 
从那时起,

15
00:01:33,406 --> 00:01:35,762
I watched the workmen do every little thing,
我看着那些工人们做每件活儿,

16
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:36,996
no matter how small.
无论多么小的事.

17
00:01:37,198 --> 00:01:39,107
After all, how else will I know...
不然的话,我怎么知道...

18
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,637
And look at this carpet.
瞧着地毯.

19
00:01:43,043 --> 00:01:43,996
I don't like carpets.
我不喜欢地毯.

20
00:01:44,248 --> 00:01:46,500
You see people covering beautiful wood floors.
你看人们把漂亮的木地板盖住.

21
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,533
It makes no sense whatsoever...
这简直没有道理...

22
00:01:49,999 --> 00:01:51,939
I'll have the architect send you the plans.
我会叫建筑师给你们拿图纸来.

23
00:01:52,917 --> 00:01:54,704
-Ms.Kovak   -Oh, Klara.
-Kovak女士  -Oh,叫我Klara好了.

24
00:01:55,150 --> 00:01:55,500
Klara. 
Klara.

25
00:01:56,919 --> 00:01:58,549
I'm sorry. I thought the phone was off. 
对不起.我以为手机关了.

26
00:01:58,761 --> 00:01:59,383
Excuse me.
失陪一下.

27
00:02:00,490 --> 00:02:01,555
As I was saying...
正如我刚才所说的...

28
00:02:02,972 --> 00:02:04,707
Hello. Hi. 
喂.你好.

29
00:02:05,332 --> 00:02:07,588
I'm in a meeting, but keep talking.
我正在开会,不过你接着说吧.

30
00:02:07,823 --> 00:02:08,495
I need the break.
我正需要休息一下.

31
00:02:08,895 --> 00:02:10,979
What's up? Who? 
发生什么事了?谁?

32
00:02:13,958 --> 00:02:15,054
She asked you what?
她让你做什么?

33
00:02:17,502 --> 00:02:18,708
What did you say?
你怎么说的?

34
00:02:23,102 --> 00:02:27,680
Wow. OK, honey. I'll see you tonight.
Wow.好,亲爱的.我们晚上见.

35
00:02:38,402 --> 00:02:40,235
We'd love you to come to our office.
非常欢迎你来我们办公室.

36
00:02:40,857 --> 00:02:42,343
We'll call and arrange an appointment.
我们会打电话约时间的.

37
00:02:49,569 --> 00:02:49,889
Wow.
Wow.

38
00:02:52,509 --> 00:02:53,966
What were we doing in there?
我们刚才在那里干什么?

39
00:02:55,859 --> 00:02:57,220
That house is fine.
那房子已经很好了.

40
00:02:58,231 --> 00:02:59,597
What did Klara say?
Klara是怎么说的?

41
00:03:00,055 --> 00:03:02,528
"It's nice but it's not quite right."
"挺好的,但感觉不对."

42
00:03:03,755 --> 00:03:05,932
She wants us to make it right!
她想让我们把它弄对!

43
00:03:06,713 --> 00:03:08,903
Oh no!
Oh 不!

